---
export const prerender = false;
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lang = 'en';
---
<Layout title="About — Superpress" lang={lang}>
  <div class="desktop-only">
    <div class="bc"><div class="bc-in"><a href="/en">Home</a><span>›</span><span class="cur">About</span></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="mobile-only">
    <div class="m-bc"><a href="/en">Home</a><span>›</span><span style="color:var(--g800)">About</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="sec"><div class="sec-in" style="max-width:820px">
    <h1 style="font-family:var(--cond);text-transform:uppercase;font-size:28px;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:20px">About</h1>
    <p style="font-size:14.5px;color:var(--g600);line-height:1.9;margin-bottom:18px">
      Superpress was established in 2023 as a subsidiary of Simpa Elektrik, to carry out activities related to
      cable hand tools.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:14.5px;color:var(--g600);line-height:1.9;margin-bottom:18px">
      We offer the sector a range of mechanical, hydraulic, and electric hand tools used in the process of
      cutting electrical cables and compressing cable lugs to prepare them for assembly. Cable cutters that
      easily cut copper and aluminum cables, along with crimping pliers fully compatible with the cable lugs
      manufactured under Simpa Elektrik, form the foundation of our products. The quality- and customer-focused
      approach of Simpa Elektrik, under whose umbrella we operate, is also the core principle of Superpress.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:14.5px;color:var(--g600);line-height:1.9">
      We aim to reduce external dependency in our field of activity, and to manufacture, import, and export
      high-quality products in flawless compatibility with the cable lugs we produce.
    </p>
  </div></div>

  <div class="sec" style="background:var(--g50)"><div class="sec-in" style="max-width:820px">
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--cond);text-transform:uppercase;font-size:26px;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:20px">Our Quality Policy</h2>
    <p class="kalite-text">As members of SUPERPRESS ELEKTRİK MALZEMESİ SANAYİ VE TİC. LTD. ŞTİ., in order to meet customer satisfaction in the products we manufacture, we undertake to:</p>
    <ul class="kalite-list">
      <li>Establish and maintain an effective management system,</li>
      <li>Ensure the continuous improvement of our products, processes, and management system,</li>
      <li>Reinforce customer satisfaction awareness through training,</li>
      <li>Provide quality products and services by increasing the knowledge and skill level of our employees,</li>
      <li>Offer our customers the best service within a framework of honesty,</li>
      <li>Ensure that all applicable requirements are fulfilled and that the necessary resources remain available for this purpose.</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="kalite-text">Our approach to service is to keep customer satisfaction in view at every stage — order, production, and shipment — and to continually seek new ways to increase it.</p>
  </div></div>

<style>
  .kalite-text { font-size: 14.5px; color: var(--g600); line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .kalite-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 16px 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  .kalite-list li { position: relative; padding-left: 22px; font-size: 14.5px; color: var(--g600); line-height: 1.7; }
  .kalite-list li::before { content: '✓'; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0; color: var(--blue); font-weight: 700; }
</style>
</Layout>
